OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLate sunny
OL,6,Fspells as showers clear away this
OL,7,Fevening. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fsee mostly dry conditions, perhaps the
OL,9,Fodd light shower around northern
OL,10,Fcoasts. Patchy frost inland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FFairly cloudy but dry for most
OL,13,Fplaces. The best of the sunnier spells
OL,14,Fare expected early in the morning and
OL,15,Flate in the day.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,18,Fon Monday with some bright spells.
OL,19,FCloudy at times on Tuesday with a
OL,20,Fchance of showers before it becomes
OL,21,Fdry on Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
